eb|title=Inception: Has Christopher Nolan forgotten how to dream?|url=https://www.rogerebert.com/scanners/inception-has-christopher-nolan-forgotten-how-to-dream|accessdate=2019-01-24|author=|date=2010-07-17|format=|publisher=|language=en|last1=Emerson|first1=Jim|website={{link-en|RogerEbert.com|RogerEbert.com}}|archive-date=2013-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130920030258/https://www.rogerebert.com/scanners/inception-has-christopher-nolan-forgotten-how-to-dream|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有報導甚至稱《全面啟動》的導演[[克里斯托弗·诺兰|克里斯托弗·诺兰]]已經承認以《盜夢偵探》作為角色設計的靈感來源<ref>{{cite news|title=Bloody Monday Manga Creators Draw Inception Film Poster|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2010-07-20/bloody-monday-manga-creators-draw-inception-poster|access-date=2011-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110120200042/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2010-07-20/bloody-monday-manga-creators-draw-inception-poster|archive-date=2011-01-20|dead-url=no|author=|date=2010-07-20|work=|accessdate=|language=en|format=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Inception par Christopher Nolan: Interview, références, indices...|url=http://www.excessif.com/cinema/actu-cinema/dossiers/inception-par-christopher-nolan-interview-references-indices-5926972-760.html|accessdate=2010-01-04|author=|date=|format=|publisher=Excessif.com|language=fr|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100717005841/http://www.excessif.com/cinema/actu-cinema/dossiers/inception-par-christopher-nolan-interview-references-indices-5926972-760.html|archivedate=2010-07-17|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

== 改編作品 ==

2009年8月，有消息指出德國導演[[沃尔夫冈·彼得森|沃夫岡·彼得森]]有望執導本片的真人版<ref>{{Cite web|title=Wolfgang Peterson To Direct Live-Action Film of Paprika?|url=https://www.slashfilm.com/wolfgang-peterson-to-direct-live-action-film-of-paprika/|accessdate=2020-11-08|date=2009-08-11|work={{link-en|/Film|/Film}}|language=en-US|archive-date=2016-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330083605/http://www.slashfilm.com/wolfgang-peterson-to-direct-live-action-film-of-paprika/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年3月，據[[MTV|MTV]]報導，彼得森已經在籌備當中。彼得森是在經他人推薦後觀賞到本片，覺得相當精彩，於是有了改編的念頭。他表示：「我們這邊有個年輕的寫手正在做，前不久他交出了一份具體且詳細的前期綱要。如果可行，他就會開始寫劇本，而且很快就能完成，因為綱要已經很詳盡。」彼得森希望真人版能有像《[[駭客任務|駭客任務]]》那樣的規模，面向更為大眾化。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Wolfgang Petersen's Live-Action 'Paprika' Adaptation Is On 'The Fast Track'|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2596258/wolfgang-petersen-paprika-adaptation/|accessdate=2020-11-08|last=Warmoth|first=Brian|work=[[音樂電視網|MTV News]]|language=en|archive-date=2018-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180118155543/http://www.mtv.com/news/2596258/wolfgang-petersen-paprika-adaptation/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Wolfgang Peterson Talks About His Live-Action Adaptation of Paprika|url=https://www.slashfilm.com/wolfgang-peterson-talks-about-his-live-action-adaptation-of-paprika/|accessdate=2020-11-08|date=2010-03-25|work={{link-en|/Film|/Film}}|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181011133303/https://www.slashfilm.com/wolfgang-peterson-talks-about-his-live-action-adaptation-of-paprika/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

